# Office365 OAuth: https://login.microsoftonline.com/common/oauth2/v2.0/authorize?client_id=YOUR_CLIENT_ID&response_type=code&redirect_uri=https://travelcheck.xyz/auth/oauth-callback?provider=office365&scope=offline_access%20Mail.Read&response_mode=query
